<li><strong>Struggle</strong>:¬†Many GTEs are having a hard time keeping up with incoming translation <a href="https://make.wordpress.org/polyglots/?resolved=unresolved&amp;tags=editor-requests">validation and PTE requests</a>.</li>
<li><strong>Big Win</strong>:¬†Made some progress in locale research and reassigning new GTEs.</li>
